name: cat rancher
description:
You are a cat rancher! But your cats ran loose. You need to recapture them all. Place fences around all the free roaming cats.

Post your personal best time into the comments!

Controls:

Move: w, a, s, d

Throw food: right click

Throw fence: left click

Dash: Shift

Place fence: Spacebar

Cancel action: c

(Fullscreen will only work after you click once)

("Ctrl" + "-" to see full artwork ;))
